OL,3,CTwo arrested and thousands of
OL,4,Ccigarettes, vapes and tobacco seized
OL,6,FTens of thousands of cigarettes,
OL,7,Fstolen tobacco and other items have
OL,8,Fbeen seized from three convenience
OL,9,Fstores in Bristol.
OL,11,FThe seizures were part of a multi-
OL,12,Fagency operation involving Avon and
OL,13,FSomerset Police, Trading Standards,
OL,14,FHMRC and The Home Office targeting
OL,15,Fcriminality and exploitation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
