OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777486270
OL,3,CTwo arrested and thousands of
OL,4,Ccigarettes, vapes and tobacco seized
OL,6,FOne man, in his twenties, was arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of being concerned in the
OL,8,Fevasion of duty has been released
OL,9,Funder investigation.
OL,11,FImmigration officials arrested a man,
OL,12,Fin his mid-twenties, on suspicion of
OL,13,Fboth working and entering the UK
OL,14,Fillegally and he has been placed on
OL,15,Fimmigration bail and will now be
OL,16,Frequired to regularly report to the
OL,17,FHome Office.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
