CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777486270
OL,3,CTwo arrested and thousands of
OL,4,Ccigarettes, vapes and tobacco seized
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police
OL,7,FNeighbourhoods' Inspector Richard
OL,8,FJones said: "The day of action was
OL,9,Fpart of our continuous work to protect
OL,10,Fthe public from harm and exploitation,
OL,11,Fand to ensure our communities are safe
OL,12,Fplaces to live and work.
OL,14,F"We hope this demonstrates and assures
OL,15,Four communities that a similar,
OL,16,Fsuccessful operation carried out in
OL,17,FFishponds last month was not a one-off
OL,18,Fand we will continue to root out
OL,19,Funscrupulous businesses in other areas
OL,20,Fof the city.
OL,26,@pD@MOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
