PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777486270
OL,3,CTwo arrested and thousands of
OL,4,Ccigarettes, vapes and tobacco seized
OL,6,F"Businesses involved in criminality is
OL,7,Fnot an issue exclusive to Bristol, but
OL,8,Fit is nonetheless a problem here which
OL,9,Fwe continue to hear concerns from
OL,10,Fmembers of the public about, and we
OL,11,Fwould urge them to continue to report
OL,12,Fissues to us so we can take the
OL,13,Fnecessary action to bring offenders to
OL,14,Fjustice."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Home Office
OL,17,Fsaid: "A business was served with a
OL,18,FCivil Penalty Referral Notice and
OL,19,Ffurther inquiries to establish any
OL,20,Fliability will now take place.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]yD@GOU
