OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1777486270
OL,3,CTwo arrested and thousands of
OL,4,Ccigarettes, vapes and tobacco seized
OL,6,F"A liable employer could face a fine
OL,7,Fof up to #45,000 per illegal worker
OL,8,Ffor a first breach and up to a maximum
OL,9,Fof #60,000 for repeat offending if
OL,10,Fit's found they employed illegal
OL,11,Fworkers and failed to conduct relevant
OL,12,Fpre-employment checks."
